Aggregation.SQLExpression: "N$10045" as (SELECT t0."CUST_ID", t0."AMOUNT_SOLD_SUM", t0."QUANTITY_SOLD_AVG" FROM (SELECT "CUST_ID", CAST(COLLECT(DM_NESTED_NUMERICAL(ID1, "AMOUNT_SOLD_SUM")) AS DM_NESTED_NUMERICALS ) "AMOUNT_SOLD_SUM", CAST(COLLECT(DM_NESTED_NUMERICAL(ID1, "QUANTITY_SOLD_AVG")) AS DM_NESTED_NUMERICALS ) "QUANTITY_SOLD_AVG" FROM (SELECT "CUST_ID", ("PROD_ID") ID1, SUM("AMOUNT_SOLD") "AMOUNT_SOLD_SUM", AVG("QUANTITY_SOLD") "QUANTITY_SOLD_AVG" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} GROUP BY "CUST_ID", (("PROD_ID")) ) GROUP BY "CUST_ID") t0 )
